{"content": "I need to multiply 483 \u00d7 233 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 483 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 483\u2081\u2081 = 4\u00d711\u00b2 + 8\u00d711\u00b9 + 3\u00d711\u2070\n- = 4\u00d7121 + 8\u00d711 + 3\u00d71\n- = 484 + 88 + 3\n- = 575\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 233 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 233\u2081\u2081 = 2\u00d711\u00b2 + 3\u00d711\u00b9 + 3\u00d711\u2070\n- = 2\u00d7121 + 3\u00d711 + 3\u00d71\n- = 242 + 33 + 3\n- = 278\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 575 \u00d7 278 = 159,850\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 159,850 (base 10) to base 11**\n- 159,850 \u00f7 11 = 14,531 R 9\n- 14,531 \u00f7 11 = 1,321 R 0\n- 1,321 \u00f7 11 = 120 R 1\n- 120 \u00f7 11 = 10 R 10 (a)\n- 10 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 10 (a)\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: aa109\n\n**Answer: aa109**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 387}